      "pos": [40, 470],
      "size": [360, 200],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 11,
      "mode": 0,
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": ["═══ WHY TWO MODELS? ═══\n\n1. CheckpointLoaderSimple:\n   Loads SDXL BASE model\n   → Provides diffusion architecture\n   → Juggernaut-XL recommended\n\n2. SUPIRModelLoaderMultiGPU:\n   Loads SUPIR ENHANCEMENT model\n   → Merges with SDXL above\n   → SUPIR-v0F = Fidelity (sharp)\n   → SUPIR-v0Q = Quality (smooth)\n\nSUPIR needs SDXL to work!"]
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [410, 250],
      "size": [360, 180],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 12,
      "mode": 0,
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": ["═══ SUPIRModelLoaderMultiGPU ═══\n\n▶ supir_model: SUPIR-v0F_fp16\n  v0F = Fidelity (preserve details)\n  v0Q = Quality (smoother output)\n\n▶ compute_device: cuda:0\n  Which GPU to use (cuda:0, cuda:1)\n\n▶ diffusion_dtype: auto\n  auto/bf16/fp16/fp32\n\n▶ fp8_unet: false\n  true = saves 50% VRAM\n  false = better quality"]
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [800, 240],
      "size": [300, 200],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 13,
      "mode": 0,
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": ["═══ SUPIRFirstStageMultiGPU ═══\n\n▶ encoder_dtype: auto\n  auto/bf16/fp32\n\n▶ use_tiled_vae: true\n  true = saves VRAM\n  false = faster but needs more VRAM\n\n▶ encoder_tile_size: 512\n  Smaller = less VRAM\n  256-1024\n\n▶ decoder_tile_size: 512\n  Smaller = less VRAM\n  256-1024"]
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [1140, 420],
      "size": [400, 180],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 14,
      "mode": 0,
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": ["═══ SUPIRConditionerMultiGPU ═══\n\n▶ positive_prompt: (from FidelityPrompts)\n  Custom positive prompt text\n\n▶ negative_prompt: (from FidelityPrompts)\n  Custom negative prompt text\n\n▶ fidelity_preset: facial_detail\n  Options:\n  • none = use custom prompts only\n  • skin_realistic = natural skin\n  • lighting_enhanced = better lighting\n  • facial_detail = face focus\n  • full_fidelity = maximum detail"]
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [1480, 560],
      "size": [350, 400],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 15,
      "mode": 0,
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": ["═══ SUPIRSamplerMultiGPU ═══\n\n▶ seed: 0\n  Random seed (change for variety)\n\n▶ steps: 15\n  15=fast | 30=balanced | 45=best\n\n▶ cfg_scale_start: 4.0\n  Prompt influence at START\n\n▶ cfg_scale_end: 4.0\n  Prompt influence at END\n\n▶ EDM_s_churn: 5\n  Noise injection (0-40)\n  Higher = more creative\n\n▶ s_noise: 1.003\n  Keep near 1.0\n\n▶ control_scale_start: 1.0\n  ⚠️ MUST BE 1.0!\n  0 = BLANK IMAGE!\n\n▶ control_scale_end: 1.0\n  ⚠️ MUST BE 1.0!\n\n▶ sampler: RestoreDPMPP2MSampler\n  TiledRestoreDPMPP2MSampler for high-res"]
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [1870, 220],
      "size": [280, 180],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 16,
      "mode": 0,
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": ["═══ SUPIRDecodeMultiGPU ═══\n\n▶ use_tiled_vae: true\n  true = saves VRAM\n  false = faster\n\n▶ decoder_tile_size: 512\n  Smaller = less VRAM\n  256-1024\n\n▶ decoder_dtype: auto\n  auto/bf16/fp32"]
    },
